[quote=“HC Kush, post:1, topic:389850”][center]when i try go to cmd prompt and put in “ipconfig” it says, [/center] [center]" ‘ipconfig’ is not recognoized as an internal or external command, operable prgram or batch file. "[/center]

[center]Adminstrator on my server[/center][/quote]

One or more of these scenarios is true:

[ul][] You somehow messed up your environment variables.
[] A virus is preventing you from executing any commands (happened to me a few years ago)
[*] You’re not in the directory that the ipconfig executable is.[/ul]
